service: instagram-api

provider:
  name: aws
  runtime: python3.8
  region: ap-south-1
  stage: dev
  memorySize: 512  # अधिक मेमोरी बेहतर परफॉरमेंस के लिए
  timeout: 30
  environment:
    SCRAPER_API_KEY: ${env:SCRAPER_API_KEY}
    SCRAPINGDOG_API_KEY: ${env:SCRAPINGDOG_API_KEY}
    REDIS_URL: ${env:REDIS_URL}

functions:
  api:
    handler: main.handler
    events:
      - http:
          path: /api/scrape
          method: post
      - http:
          path: /health
          method: get

plugins:
  - serverless-python-requirements

custom:
  pythonRequirements:
    dockerizePip: true
    useStaticCache: true
